  "instructions": [
    "Chop the Manchego cheese into small cubes.",
    "Combine the lemon juice, mint leaves, grated Parmesan, salt, and olive oil in a mixing bowl until well combined. Stir gently to ensure all ingredients are evenly distributed.",
    "Add the Manchego cheese cubes to the mixture and mix thoroughly.",
    "Place the mixture on a baking dish lined with parchment paper for easy cleanup.",
    "Bake at 350°F (175°C) for about 20 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Let cool slightly before serving."
